jtUbgdYSC_8_5zj6UMkNw">Tập Linh đài kỳ 2 - 集靈臺其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%97/author-uSefdg6gWPnl7XHeM-UXCw">Trương Hỗ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Bang-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/Thu%E1%BB%B5-long-ng%C3%A2m/poem-zHB68a6tsnkHiLwQbCQG3Q">Thuỵ long ngâm - 瑞龍吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Bang-Ng%E1%BA%A1n/author-aRbK_iKDMX5ibYXonb22rA">Chu Bang Ngạn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-dUPCCAAa0N5bTyEhEmiB1w">Tòng quân hành - 從軍行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-H%E1%BB%A3p/T%E1%BB%AB-B%E1%BA%A1ch-t%C3%A2n-kh%C3%A1ch-quy-h%E1%BA%ADu-k%C3%BD/poem-q3uLjf8u5-Vhs_UbHI4OYQ">Từ Bạch tân khách quy hậu ký - 辭白賓客歸後寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Di%C3%AAu-H%E1%BB%A3p/author-vs3gFjAvih8Xq3PRsiAJTg">Diêu Hợp</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-M%E1%BA%A1nh-C%E1%BB%91c-tr%C3%B9ng-ch%C3%AD-%C4%91%C3%B4-m%C3%B4n/poem-CwBOSFQlHwxVlqeKYRSZGg">Vương Mạnh Cốc trùng chí đô môn - 王孟榖重至都門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tra-Th%E1%BA%ADn-H%C3%A0nh/author-9xzWBLqDsfopprRgu6Tsgg">Tra Thận Hành</a>)<br></div>	</div>
